Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.68,0:00:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,放馬過來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.98,0:00:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,所以懲罰就是命令他們兩人去買點心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.23,0:00:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.11,0:00:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是說他們兩個\N在這麼冷的天裡去買東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.70,0:00:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.95,0:00:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,今天天氣可是很冷的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.78,0:00:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,話說妳的穿著看起來也很不保暖耶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.29,0:00:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒問題喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.46,0:00:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,古泉同學真可憐…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.79,0:00:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,阿虛就不要緊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我來打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.59,0:00:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.09,0:00:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是實玖瑠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.72,0:00:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.93,0:00:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,如果想調戲實玖瑠…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.48,0:00:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,就要先打倒我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.81,0:00:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是說妳想跟我一戰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.15,0:00:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.61,0:00:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,禁止在社團教室裡戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.91,0:01:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,對吧 社長？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.87,0:01:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.45,0:01:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,因為實玖瑠很可愛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.79,0:01:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我懂妳的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.38,0:01:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,妳懂嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.63,0:01:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,要是實玖瑠掉在自動販賣機旁邊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.21,0:01:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,會想要撿起來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.22,0:01:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那是把我比喻成小貓還是零錢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.97,0:01:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.85,0:01:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,談論可愛東西的話題
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.60,0:01:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,居然沒提到我家的長門同學
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.18,0:01:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼要比這種事？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.85,0:01:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我就接受妳的挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.23,0:01:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 我接受
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.90,0:01:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,在長門同學睡覺的時候去跟她講話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.11,0:01:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,她會叫我「媽媽」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.24,0:01:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣會感冒的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.20,0:01:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽 再讓我睡一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.11,0:01:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？那不是假設的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.07,0:01:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,難道妳講的是真話嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.95,0:01:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.66,0:01:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,實玖瑠追貓的時候會撞到電線桿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.87,0:01:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,望著天空的時候會掉進水溝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.33,0:01:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,而且還百發百中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.13,0:01:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.79,0:01:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,別說得我好像每天都會發生這些事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.63,0:01:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然我偶爾會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.21,0:01:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,這算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.05,0:01:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,長門每天會在浴室的鏡子前\N看著自己的肚子…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.80,0:01:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼要說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼要說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.76,0:02:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,現在不是要比誰丟臉對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.72,0:02:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,既然妳連這都說了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.97,0:02:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就拿出壓箱寶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.93,0:02:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,其實實玖瑠的胸上有顆星形的痣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,出現我不知道的情報了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,還真的有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,鶴屋學姊還真是有一套
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.86,0:02:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,居然說出連本人都不知道的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.16,0:02:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.66,0:02:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,再這樣下去就要輸囉？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,別再煽風點火了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.83,0:02:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,朝倉同學 這樣就夠了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.71,0:02:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,妳不知道其他怪事了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,有啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.71,0:02:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,長門同學為了迎接即將到來的情人節
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.09,0:02:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,偷偷買好材料藏起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.72,0:02:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,歡度節慶也是好事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.31,0:02:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,這件事沒什麼好難為情的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,根本沒必要偷偷做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:03:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,就是說啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.22,0:03:24.43,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}ナゾナゾみたいな恋してみるかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:26.97,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}星が囁く
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:29.89,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}怖いけど…ありかな！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.39,0:03:35.36,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}なんとなく生きてる　なんてつまらない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.52,0:03:40.11,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}本当は何かを変えてみたいのです
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.11,0:03:43.82,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}きっかけが欲しいから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.99,0:03:45.49,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}飛んで飛んでBoooon！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:49.66,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}思い出が騒いでる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:55.25,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}私…あなたを知ってるみたい！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:59.38,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}晴れても雨でも雪の日でも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:02.13,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}会いに会いに行っちゃいたい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:03.55,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}ムカシ→ミライ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.68,0:04:04.80,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}アシタ→ミライ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:07.68,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}そうだね　時はNonstop
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.89,0:04:13.48,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}ちょっと前に悩んでたこと　みんなみんな消しちゃって
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:19.36,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}新しい物語　始めましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:24.45,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}また夢見てる？いまの夢はまだ秘密！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:27.28,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}晴れ晴れよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:29.95,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}降れ降れよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:35.04,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}どんな天気だって I need you！！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.22,0:03:24.43,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}想試著談場猜謎般的戀愛嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:26.97,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}星星在呢喃著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:29.89,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}雖然害怕…但還是想！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.39,0:03:35.36,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}光是安穩度日 也太無趣了點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.52,0:03:40.11,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}真希望能改變些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.11,0:03:43.82,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}既然想要個契機
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.99,0:03:45.49,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}那就飛奔出去吧 Boooon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:49.66,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}回憶在騷動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:55.25,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}我…好像認識你！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:59.38,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}不論是晴天雨天還是在下雪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:02.13,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}我都好想好想去見你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:03.55,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}從過去到未來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.68,0:04:04.80,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}從明天到未來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:07.68,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}是啊 時間 Nonstop
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.89,0:04:13.48,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}先前煩惱的事情 通通都消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:19.36,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}來展開新的故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:24.45,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}又在做夢嗎？現在的夢還不能說！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:27.28,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}大晴天也好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:29.95,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}下雨天也好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:35.04,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}不管是怎樣的天氣 I need you!!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,平安時代的戀愛很講究家世財力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.30,0:04:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,最重要的是如果和歌寫得不好\N就不會受歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.93,0:04:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs80}會這樣是因為當時的戀愛是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.68,0:04:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs80}藉由和歌往來書信而開始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs80}要先認同對方寫和歌的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,阿虛同學 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.23,0:04:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,還蠻痛的 有什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:04:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs80}才終於能夠進展到約會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 今天呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:05.95,Note,,0,0,0,,情人節手作甜點特集
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.32,0:05:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,要求得拋物線跟直線交點的座標…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.92,0:05:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.17,0:05:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,特地跑來校門前等我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,還真是相當體貼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.01,0:05:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？只有妳一個人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,古泉呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.72,0:05:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他似乎有委員會的工作所以來不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 那正好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,朝倉和長門似乎也有要事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.93,0:05:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,光我一個人去社團教室也很無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.35,0:05:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,所以今天社團活動休息一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,於是乎為了別讓妳闖進學校
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.82,0:05:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我就在這裡等妳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.91,0:05:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,居然不跟本部長商量就擅自休息…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.33,0:05:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,妳這非法社員在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.66,0:05:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 今天是13號
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:05:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,難怪要休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.67,0:06:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那邊的年輕人請留步
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,這位女學生有什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,少廢話 總之跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不 所以說…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.93,0:06:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.56,0:06:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 要去哪裡啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.40,0:06:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,雖說我想趕緊動手開始做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不過材料還真是多呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不是有句話叫作\N「只要耐心等待就會有好報」嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那句話已經太老舊了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.83,0:06:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不 這不是新舊的問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,依我來看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,被說成是不可思議的現象
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是不會那麼容易出現的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,正因為這樣才有去尋找它的價值
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.38,0:06:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,所以說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,必須由我們主動去把\N不可思議的事情找出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:06:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:07:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那些「好報」也肯定\N一直在等我們把它們找出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,有可能這些「好報」\N尋求的是平靜與安穩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.90,0:07:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我們去找出這世上不可思議的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.03,0:07:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,要上哪找？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,天知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.37,0:07:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,這你就不懂了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道也有不知道的找法喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.87,0:07:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,懂了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,完全不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.80,0:07:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,總之我們就腳踏實地開始探索市區吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你將會成為開拓嶄新歷史的人喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,夠了 隨妳高興啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 這樣就準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,話說我還沒問妳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.82,0:07:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,妳打算做怎樣的巧克力？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,光看這些材料\N似乎不是要做太複雜的東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.82,0:07:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:07:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.70,0:08:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,總之融化 倒進去 撒上去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,等凝固以後就變巧克力了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,該怎麼說 分明是非常簡單的步驟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.25,0:08:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但若是讓她一個人做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺好像會失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.26,0:08:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,簡潔明瞭雖然很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.59,0:08:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,但要不要再下點功夫？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,比方說做個心型巧克力蛋糕之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,心…不用做到那樣…沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.31,0:08:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,太過簡單的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,就沒有我能幫上忙的地方了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.44,0:08:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,也罷 那就趕快來融巧克力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.30,0:08:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,妳沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:08:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,長門同學加油
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.27,0:09:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好 暫停
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,馬上就出錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.40,0:09:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡得使用隔水加熱的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,隔水加熱？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.45,0:09:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不這麼做就沒辦法順利融化了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.99,0:09:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害 真的融化了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,果然有很多地方需要我幫忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,到底在哪裡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂喂 那可是二月的河水耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 妳這樣會感冒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.52,0:09:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多該上岸了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.44,0:09:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,再一下下 等我找到河童
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.24,0:09:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,妳呆子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.86,0:09:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,別走到太深的地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.11,0:10:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,萬一滑倒可是會死的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.24,0:10:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不要緊 不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.91,0:10:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.62,0:10:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好險
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.91,0:10:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我說妳真的不要緊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.58,0:10:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,真拿妳沒轍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.76,0:10:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你幹麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.76,0:10:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,真是體貼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.56,0:10:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.89,0:10:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,春日
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.79,0:10:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.63,0:10:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你雙腳好像很冷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.42,0:10:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,原來妳知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.01,0:10:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,給我記住了 妳這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.13,0:11:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我會記恨的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,大概是這種感覺吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.56,0:11:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,做得很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.53,0:11:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我說阿虛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.33,0:11:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得河童真的存在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,天知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.79,0:11:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,也許有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.34,0:11:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,春日？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.76,0:11:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,春日
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.26,0:11:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,已經夠了吧 我們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.94,0:11:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 區區個阿虛別走在我前面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛 那算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:11:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,明天要去哪裡探索？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.07,0:12:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,完成了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那就放進冰箱等它們凝固囉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.83,0:12:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不行不行 不可以熬夜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.57,0:12:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,所以妳又照例因為睡不著玩起遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.07,0:12:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,等回神時天已經亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.74,0:12:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,妳這孩子真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,趕快給我去洗臉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:13:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,長門同學 動作快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.52,0:13:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,長門同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.14,0:13:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我馬上來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是說妳什麼時候要把巧克力給他？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.07,0:13:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.53,0:13:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,果然還是社團活動的時間吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.87,0:13:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.91,0:13:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,就得製造讓你們兩人獨處的空間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,兩人獨處？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 把阿虛同學叫出來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.25,0:13:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺難度好高
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.71,0:13:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,打起精神來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.25,0:13:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不管用什麼方法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,想把巧克力交給他本來就有難度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,才多上一兩個依然很簡單啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.97,0:13:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,問題在那裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.76,0:13:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,反正不管難度增加多少
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,妳還是會把那個送給他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我會送出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,情人節終於來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.37,0:14:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,真奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,阿虛你說是不是搞錯了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,谷口 過度期待會帶來更深的失望喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.17,0:14:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,今天的午餐是巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,真奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.05,0:14:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,阿虛你說是不是搞錯了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.55,0:14:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,谷口 死心能防止自己\N受到不必要的傷害喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,長門唷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,妳好 要去吃午餐嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.73,0:14:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,妳怎麼沒跟朝瞄在一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,鶴屋同學 不要突然就跑起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟朝倉同學說好在社團教室碰面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.87,0:14:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,今天就在文藝社吃午餐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,實玖瑠沒問題吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我是沒問題啦 在那之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我們可以去打擾嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.05,0:15:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,沒間題 沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.10,0:15:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.51,0:15:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我們今天待在教室會提心吊膽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.18,0:15:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺會吃不下飯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.85,0:15:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,提心吊膽？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.27,0:15:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,今天不就是情人節嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.65,0:15:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,男生們的眼神都變了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.23,0:15:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,鶴屋同學 妳說得太誇張了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.03,0:15:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.41,0:15:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣下去要是連一個巧克力都不送
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.41,0:15:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,可是會演變成不可收拾的局面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.20,0:15:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟實玖瑠的粉絲俱樂部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.12,0:15:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,可是有上百名會員呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,知道的真是詳細…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他們該不會有準備巧克力吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,妳為什麼不否認？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.09,0:15:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…雖說是很理所當然的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.31,0:15:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不過收到的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.56,0:16:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,會期待喜歡的人送自己巧克力嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,當然會期待了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.44,0:16:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,本來就是為此才存在的節慶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.98,0:16:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,裝作一副不在意的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.86,0:16:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,就證明那個人其實很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.82,0:16:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那所以拿到其他人送的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.45,0:16:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,就只會讓本人感到困擾了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.20,0:16:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不 沒那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.87,0:16:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,也許是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,鶴屋同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,因為是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.67,0:16:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,所以當然會有喜歡 普通\N以及討厭等等的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不過那種事根本無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.51,0:16:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,因為這本來就是送的人\N單方面的自我滿足
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.51,0:16:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,所以就當作是為了自己而送就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,用不著在意對方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.35,0:16:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,就盡情扔到對方懷中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.98,0:16:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不能用扔的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕 我忘記買飲料了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.16,0:16:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我去買一下 妳們就先吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.08,0:17:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,她應該很快就回來了 我們先吃吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.25,0:17:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.84,0:17:17.80,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an2\fn華康方圓體W7\fsp10\shad8.5\c&HF2C4EE&\3c&H9F4765&\4c&HA36379&\4a255\iclip(699,984,1246,1065)\t(27,694,\iclip(1246,984,1244,1065))}不說話光吃飯的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.22,0:17:20.68,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an2\fn華康方圓體W7\fsp10\shad8.5\c&HD0C5FC&\3c&H7158A6&\4c&H5A4BD2&\4a255\iclip(736,982,1208,1064)\t(26,484,\iclip(1208,982,1208,1064))}似乎很焦慮的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我說那個啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.56,0:17:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,剛剛鶴屋同學是在鼓勵妳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.98,0:17:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對不是在欺負妳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.49,0:17:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.99,0:17:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…雖然她說話的方式很極端
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.53,0:17:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 如果換成我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.08,0:17:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定會很高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.37,0:17:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,因為如果我是男生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.17,0:17:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,收到長門學妹的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.97,0:17:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對會很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼好像變成我在告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.77,0:18:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,沒辦法好好表達 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不會 謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 這位太太妳聽見了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,清清楚楚地聽見了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.57,0:18:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那怎麼看都像是告白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.28,0:18:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,實玖瑠？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然這話有點難開口 但…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.33,0:18:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,長門的心裡已經住著阿虛了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.33,0:18:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,招來了天大的誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼要偷聽？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.67,0:18:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟鶴屋學姊在途中碰到就一起過來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.72,0:18:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,結果看到妳們兩個像\N少女漫畫那樣對望 不小心就…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.51,0:18:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,然後我們就用眼神交流
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.22,0:18:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,決定「就這樣在旁邊看著她們兩個吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.02,0:18:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,也許這兩人的思考模式是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.11,0:18:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,就像是寶塚歌劇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.03,0:18:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.32,0:18:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.28,0:19:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.36,0:19:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,受到學姊們的鼓舞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.28,0:19:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,多少有點勇氣了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,決戰時刻就在放學後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.08,0:19:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們就先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.13,0:19:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.59,0:19:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝妳們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.60,0:19:29.60,Note,,0,0,0,,情人節大作戰！!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.01,0:19:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼現在就開始講述今天的作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.02,0:19:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,仔細聽好囉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.06,0:19:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.10,0:19:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,首先 長門同學妳吧\N社團教室的鑰匙拿出來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.61,0:19:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,放學後我會把這支鑰匙交給阿虛同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.90,0:19:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,請他去開社團教室的門
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.12,0:19:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.99,0:19:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs80}我開門囉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.91,0:19:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,然後在阿虛同學打開教室門的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.91,0:19:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,妳再過去的話 接著不可思議的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.87,0:19:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs80}請收下這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.87,0:19:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,社團教室就變成你跟阿虛同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs80}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,兩人獨處的空間了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.46,0:19:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:19:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,而在那之後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.26,0:20:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我會晚一點才去社團教室
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.01,0:20:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.09,0:20:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂喂 妳現在就這麼緊張怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.43,0:20:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不要緊吧？真的做得到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？不過不用繞這麼一大圈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.56,0:20:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我趕快去社團教室
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.73,0:20:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,在那裡等他不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.69,0:20:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,長門同學 妳仔細想想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.57,0:20:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得由自己決定何時進入\N有阿虛同學在的教室裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.74,0:20:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,還是在教室裡戰戰兢兢地等著\N不知何時才會來的阿虛同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.00,0:20:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,哪一種情況妳會比較有心理準備？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.55,0:20:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我選自己進去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.59,0:20:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,所以說即使要多花一點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.51,0:20:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,也要做好心理準備再送出去喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.39,0:20:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.19,0:21:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟那是妳拼命竭盡心力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.90,0:21:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,所做出的巧克力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.53,0:21:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.20,0:21:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.62,0:21:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我被踢進名為「失望」的地獄了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.38,0:21:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你還好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,國木田…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.92,0:21:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我也只有收到人情巧克力喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.18,0:21:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.85,0:21:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,就盡情扔到對方懷中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.48,0:21:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對會很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.77,0:21:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟那是妳拼命竭盡心力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.19,0:21:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,所做出的巧克力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.68,0:22:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉我來遲了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.16,0:22:42.04,ED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(198,198)}名前を呼ばれただけで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.25,0:22:48.59,ED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(198,198)}胸が熱くなるの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:53.72,ED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(198,198)}近くにいるしあわせ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.97,0:22:58.77,ED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(198,198)}ああ手放せない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.10,0:23:06.15,ED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(198,198)}恋は優しい風を連れてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.61,0:23:12.12,ED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(198,198)}あしたを夢見る風を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.53,0:23:18.37,ED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(198,198)}伝えたいときめきが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.66,0:23:24.54,ED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(198,198)}私を変えたの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.96,0:23:30.55,ED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(198,198)}言葉が出てこないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.01,0:23:36.68,ED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(198,198)}いつか伝えなくちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.81,0:23:42.56,ED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(198,198)}ありがとう　だいすき
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.85,0:23:52.66,ED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(198,198)}もう少しこのままでいさせて
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.16,0:22:42.04,ED - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(198,198)}光是聽見你呼喚我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.25,0:22:48.59,ED - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(198,198)}胸口就開始發燙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:53.72,ED - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(198,198)}近在咫尺的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.97,0:22:58.77,ED - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(198,198)}啊　我不會鬆手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.10,0:23:06.15,ED - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(198,198)}戀愛帶來溫柔的清風
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.61,0:23:12.12,ED - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(198,198)}那是夢想著明日的清風
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.53,0:23:18.37,ED - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(198,198)}想要傳遞出的這份悸動
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.66,0:23:24.54,ED - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(198,198)}改變了原先的我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.96,0:23:30.55,ED - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(198,198)}雖然現在還不知該如何表達
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.01,0:23:36.68,ED - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(198,198)}但總有一天一定要對你說
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.81,0:23:42.56,ED - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(198,198)}謝謝你　最喜歡你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.85,0:23:52.66,ED - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(198,198)}現在就暫且維持現狀吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
